<ITEM><HI>Semi-pelagians,</HI> their axiom, <HI>Facienti quod in &s;e e&s;t Deus non denega<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> gratiam,</HI> 127.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Servant</HI>; whether it be lawful to &s;ay, I am your Humble Servant, 524.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Servetus,</HI> 505.</ITEM>
