<ITEM><HI>Truth</HI>; there is a differ|ence betwixt what one &s;aith of the Truth, and that which the Truth it &s;elf, interpret|ing it &s;elf, &s;aith, 21. Truth is not hard to be arrived at, but is mo&s;t nigh, 21.</ITEM>
